title: Lets Make HDN new IFO?
body:
Well we count with you community to make hodlers Network the New IFO of pancake Swap, 
Hodlers Network is a service that allows to verify users and to prevent fraud. It is based on BSC blockchain technology as a tool for protecting and validating personal data of Crypro users.
Check our website hodlers.network  and all our medias 
Vote yes Guys we count on you
